22:43.963 --> 22:49.168 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Adding to the fear, an Italian
student was
found dead just last week, his
body tortured.

22:49.268 --> 22:55.174 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In total, 40,000 political
prisoners fill
Egypt's jails. Hundreds, perhaps
thousands

22:55.274 --> 22:59.144 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
more have disappeared into
secret prisons.

22:59.245 --> 23:03.849 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The government crackdown peaked
last month
in downtown Cairo. This has long
been the

23:03.949 --> 23:08.520 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
epicenter for people who oppose
the government.
And this used to be full of
cafes. You can

23:08.621 --> 23:14.059 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
