now, clearly
designed to send the message
that nobody was

23:14.159 --> 23:16.929 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
allowed the space to meet or
organize.

23:17.029 --> 23:20.532 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
In today's Egypt, is there
freedom of speech?

23:20.633 --> 23:25.471 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MUSTAFA MAHER, Egypt (through
translator):
It's completely disappeared.
Either you're

23:25.571 --> 23:29.975 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
a Sisi supporter and you can
freely talk,
or you oppose him even in a
limited way, like

23:30.075 --> 23:37.683 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
a Facebook profile picture or on
Twitter,
and you will be brought to
justice.

23:37.783 --> 23:42.021 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Mustafa Maher is
the brother
of Ahmed Maher, one of Egypt's
best-known

23:42.121 --> 23:50.062 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
