23:51.997 --> 23:55.534 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AMAL SHARAF: "Dear Ahmed Maher,
we call for
your immediate and unconditional
release."

23:55.634 --> 24:00.172 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: But, today,
Maher's admirers
can only write him letters. Two
years ago,

24:00.272 --> 24:05.077 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
