24:18.190 --> 24:22.161 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
REHAM IBRAHIM, Wife of Ahmed
Maher (through
translator): They don't allow
anything written,

24:22.261 --> 24:27.366 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
