Anything that
will provide any hope, they
block.

24:27.466 --> 24:33.472 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AMAL SHARAF: They know he's a
symbol for the
revolution. And he's paying the
price now.

24:33.572 --> 24:40.512 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
For what? For saying the truth,
for opposing
the oppression.

24:40.612 --> 24:46.151 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NICK SCHIFRIN: Maher's daughter,
Meral (ph),
is 8. Each time she visits her
dad in prison,

24:46.251 --> 24:50.255 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
