24:50.356 --> 24:56.261 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
REHAM IBRAHIM (through
translator): I never
imagined years would pass this
way, and I

24:56.362 --> 24:58.364 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
