parliament.

25:42.775 --> 25:46.378 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
TARIQ EL KHOULY (through
translator): We left
the political zone empty. We
should now be

25:46.478 --> 25:48.313 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
