26:15.040 --> 26:22.548 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
ABDEL RAHIM ALI, Egyptian
Parliament Member
(through translator): When the
matter has

26:22.648 --> 26:28.554 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
