31:29.788 --> 31:34.359 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But, first, yesterday America's
top intelligence
officials were on Capitol Hill
yesterday to

31:34.459 --> 31:39.131 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
