Islamic State
group, the war in Syria, North
Korea's nuclear

31:44.836 --> 31:47.873 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
activities and a resurgent
Russia.

31:47.973 --> 31:51.243 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We're joined now by David Cohen,
the deputy
director of the Central
Intelligence Agency.

31:51.343 --> 31:55.247 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He's been at the CIA for one
year, after five
years at the Treasury Department
overseeing

31:55.347 --> 31:59.117 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
sanctions implementation and
efforts to combat
terrorism financing.

31:59.217 --> 32:03.855 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, when I rattle off those
