32:06.658 --> 32:08.426 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAVID COHEN, Deputy Director,
Central Intelligence
Agency: Well, I think that was a
list of six,

32:08.527 --> 32:11.897 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
