32:11.997 --> 32:17.435 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
I mean, obviously, we're
spending a lot of
time focused on the threat from
ISIL. We're

32:17.536 --> 32:23.809 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
also very much engaged in what's
happening
in Syria and Iraq, the threat
from Russia.

32:23.909 --> 32:30.115 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And just this past weekend, we
