issues are, you know, top of the
list for

32:34.653 --> 32:36.555 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
us at the agency.

32:36.655 --> 32:40.292 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: OK. Given the
time you spent
a lot of time at Treasury
looking at sanctions,

32:40.392 --> 32:44.963 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
