there is quite a conversation
happening about

32:45.063 --> 32:46.298 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Iran after the nuclear deal.

32:46.398 --> 32:48.233 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
DAVID COHEN: Sure.

32:48.333 --> 32:51.636 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: So looking at
it now through
your lens at the CIA, what
intelligence do

32:51.736 --> 32:56.875 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
we have? How are we so confident
we can catch
Iran if they were to cheat?

32:56.975 --> 33:03.181 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAVID COHEN: Well, the Joint
Comprehensive
Plan of Action, the JCPOA, that
was agreed

33:03.281 --> 33:11.623 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to over the summer has within it
a whole series
of measures that would allow the
IAEA the

33:11.723 --> 33:18.930 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
unprecedented access to Iran's
nuclear program,
from the very -- from the
uranium mills and

33:19.030 --> 33:24.569 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
mines all the way through
whatever enrichment
facilities they may have, to
their centrifuges,

33:24.669 --> 33:30.709 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
an extraordinary window into
what Iran is
doing that the IAEA will have
and the international

33:30.809 --> 33:33.011 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
community will have.

33:33.111 --> 33:40.418 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that's one very important
part of it,
but we have also been very much
focused on

33:40.518 --> 33:46.524 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Iran's nuclear program for a
number of years,
and so we will be able to,
obviously, supplement

33:46.625 --> 33:52.764 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
what the IAEA is able to
discover through
our own efforts as well.

33:52.864 --> 33:57.135 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: What about the
