program.

34:24.896 --> 34:31.403 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So I think it's our assessment
that Iran is
intending to use the sanctions
relief, the

34:31.503 --> 34:37.676 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
vast majority of the sanctions
relief that
it will be obtaining to repair
its economy,

34:37.776 --> 34:44.549 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to try and deliver some modicum
of economic
growth to its people. And we
will be watching

34:44.649 --> 34:49.888 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
very carefully how Iran is
making use of that
money. We're watching it very
carefully.

34:49.988 --> 34:51.756 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: OK.

34:51.856 --> 34:57.595 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Let's talk a little bit about
ISIS, or ISIL.
We had a report that we saw just
today from

34:57.696 --> 35:04.102 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
