do you support
them?

35:07.172 --> 35:10.642 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAVID COHEN: Well, look, I'm not
going to
get into anything that the CIA
may or may

35:10.742 --> 35:15.513 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
