it on the chin recently, but
they have also

36:19.411 --> 36:25.083 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
been quite resilient. You know,
this conflict
has been going on now for, you
know, five

36:25.183 --> 36:27.452 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
years, close to five years.

36:27.552 --> 36:33.124 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And the moderate opposition has,
