sort of a social media presence,
are the Facebooks,

37:09.627 --> 37:13.231 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
the Googles, the Twitters of the
world helping
you in any way?

37:13.331 --> 37:18.169 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAVID COHEN: Look, I'm not going
to get into
the sort of particularities of
how we -- how,

37:18.269 --> 37:24.476 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
if we find a suspect who is on
social media,
how we're able to tap into that.

37:24.576 --> 37:30.281 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
There is an ongoing conversation
with the
media companies, some of which
we're involved

37:30.381 --> 37:35.086 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in, but also, you know, the FBI
and others
in domestic law enforcement are
very much

37:35.186 --> 37:37.088 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
engaged in this conversation.

37:37.188 --> 37:44.162 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We set up this new directorate
specifically
because we have recognized that
we need to

37:44.262 --> 37:50.368 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
do a better job of leveraging
and operating
in the digital domain. I mean, I
think your

37:50.468 --> 37:57.942 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
viewers know this as well as we
do that increasingly
we live our lives online.
Increasingly, the

37:58.042 --> 38:03.715 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
information that we have access
to is digital
information.

38:03.815 --> 38:09.420 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And we, as the Central
Intelligence Agency,
felt that we needed to do a
better job of

38:09.521 --> 38:15.927 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
both harnessing the digital
information that
we have, of thinking about how
we operate

38:16.027 --> 38:22.734 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in the digital domain, and
making sure that
we are making use of digital
technologies

38:22.834 --> 38:25.136 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
to the greatest extent possible.

38:25.236 --> 38:31.276 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Finally, I
have heard that
one of the things that you say
to the new

38:31.376 --> 38:35.547 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
