that this
is an agency that's governed by
law, right?

38:35.647 --> 38:37.382 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
DAVID COHEN: Right.

38:37.482 --> 38:39.217 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: And one of the
practices
that's very difficult for
Americans to swallow

38:39.317 --> 38:45.290 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
is drone strikes that kill
