following what American law is.

38:53.164 --> 38:55.800 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Should the CIA be in the drone
strike business?

38:55.900 --> 39:00.538 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAVID COHEN: Look, I'm not going
to comment
on whether the CIA is involved
in any of those

39:00.638 --> 39:02.640 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
sorts of activities.

39:02.740 --> 39:11.182 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I will say, however, that the
embrace of legal
constraints on what we do,
domestic law, international

39:11.282 --> 39:17.222 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
law, is something that we are
quite happy
to have and to operate within a
system of

39:17.322 --> 39:22.026 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
laws. And what makes the CIA,
what makes the
United States different from
many countries

39:22.126 --> 39:25.897 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
around the world is adherence to
the rule
of law.

39:25.997 --> 39:30.635 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, as you said, Hari, when I
swear in new
officers, one of the points I
make to them

39:30.735 --> 39:38.309 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
is that we operate within a
legal construct,
we operate within the laws, not
fighting against

39:38.409 --> 39:45.016 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
it, but willingly, happily
embracing the fact
that what we do is governed by
law. That's

39:45.116 --> 39:52.023 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
core to the CIA. It's core to
what this country
is all about, and it's not
something that

39:52.123 --> 39:53.858 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
we chafe against at all.

39:53.958 --> 39:57.662 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: All right,
David Cohen with
the CIA, thanks so much for
joining us.

39:57.762 --> 40:06.771 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
DAVID COHEN: Thank you.

40:06.871 --> 40:14.178 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: In a surprise
move late
yesterday, the U.S. Supreme
