40:19.784 --> 40:23.221 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
outcome of judicial appeals in
the lower courts.

40:23.321 --> 40:25.223 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
William Brangham has that.

40:25.323 --> 40:28.693 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: In a move
