greenhouse gas

40:33.097 --> 40:35.566 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
emissions from coal-fired power
plants.

40:35.667 --> 40:39.637 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The high court's order means
these regulations,
which were put out by the
Environmental Protection

40:39.737 --> 40:44.976 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Agency, can't go into effect
