argument against
them?

42:01.386 --> 42:08.893 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CORAL DAVENPORT: Their reason to
block the
rules is, if the rules were to
go into effect,

42:08.993 --> 42:14.132 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
