coal-fired
power plants in the U.S.

42:18.703 --> 42:24.142 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They would freeze construction
of future coal-fired
power plants and almost
certainly freeze the

42:24.242 --> 42:31.349 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
domestic market for U.S. coal.
So the coal
industry and states where coal
mining or coal-fired

42:31.449 --> 42:36.287 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
power plants are a big part of
the company
have been fighting tooth and
nail against

42:36.387 --> 42:39.190 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
