the rule.

42:56.607 --> 43:01.279 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: So, the
Supreme Court steps
in and says no implementing of
these rules

43:01.379 --> 43:06.284 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
