court stepped
in?

43:08.920 --> 43:14.926 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CORAL DAVENPORT: Yes, it's very
rare for the
court to issue a stay like this,
and almost

43:15.026 --> 43:22.099 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
unprecedented for the court to
halt a regulation
before the regulation has --
before there's

43:22.200 --> 43:26.871 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
